title: SwifTEA: Red (Taylor's Version) Is Coming!
description:
It's official!! Taylor Swift announced the next re-recorded album will be "Red (Taylor's Version)" and we are so happy, free, confused, and lonely at the same time! Nick and Ana break down the big news, the signs that pointed to Red, and more!
